## [Measurement Error]{style="color:#078BCD;"}

This is not sampling error. 

![](../img/bear.scale.png)

## [Measurement Error]{style="color:#078BCD;"}

Inaccurate measurements due to malfunctioning instruments or poor procedures or
by-product of sampling plan

E.g., The intervewier effect
  - In Aspen, CO, human black bear conflicts tend to be under-reported
  - In New Jersey, they tend to be over-reported
  - Depends on social constructs and attitudes towards wildlife
